Level 0 contains how to connect to the challege server to solve the challenge.
We use SSH to connect to the challenge server.
whatis SSH ->(SSH client) is a program for logging into a remote machine and for executing commands on a remote machine.
here our host server will be bandit.labs.overthewire.org which will listen us on port-2220
our username will be the bandit level eg for bandit 0 it will be bandit0.

